                    </div>
                    <span>I bought this book and also Fodor's Pocket Shanghai. This book has better print/paper quality. Has more maps. For each attraction, there is a color photo so that you can decide if you would like to go there. The photo also helps to identify the attraction if you do decide to go there.<BR>The Fodor's book has no photos, looks [inexpensive], but is actually [$] more.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The Best Compact Guide on Shanghai</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
