                    </div>
                    <span>I was plesantly surprised by this compact book. I didn't know that it was associated with the Discovery Channel. The book has outstanding print/paper quality. It has plenty of maps and lots of pictures. This helps me to find the place. I can also decide, from the pictures, if I would be interested in visiting such an attraction.<BR>The best surprise is that this book is actually listed [$$$] less than the Fodor's compact book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent compact guide</div>
